leep 耳塞实际上可以改善睡眠&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.theverge.com/24125032/soundcore-sleep-a20-review-noise-cancelling-耳塞&quot;},{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;Anker 的简约家用备用电池已为停电季节做好准备&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.theverge.com/24136932/anker-solix-x1-home- Battery-powerwall-alternative-specs&quot;},{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;如何在 iOS 17 上使用新的待机模式&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.theverge.com/23798104/apple-standby-mode -iphone-ios-17-clock-widgets-photos-customize-how-to&quot;}]}&#39;>;&lt;/div>;&lt;/aside>;&lt;/div>; &lt;p id=&quot;dtvS4t&quot;>;我很高兴&#39;我被迫等待采用新的磁力充电标准，因为这意味着我现在可以享受折扣，就像我们目前在 Anker 的支持 Qi2 的 MagGo 移动电源上看到的那样。 &lt;strong>;Anker MagGo 移动电源 (10K)&lt;/strong>;，10,000mAh 版本...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/5/23 /24163317/anker-maggo-power-bank-10k-6k-qi2-charger-deal-sale&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/5/23/24163317/anker-maggo-power-bank-10k-6k-qi2-charger-deal-sale" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/5/23/24163317/anker-maggo-power-bank-10k-6k-qi2-charger-deal-sale</id><author><name>昆汀·肯内默</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-05-23T16:57:58-04:00</published><updated> 2024-05-23T16:57:58-04:00</updated><title>美国国税局将其免费申报税收计划再延长五年</title><content type="html">&lt;图>; &lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/qZ93pAkY7Lj0BSHkReBZyj-NYa8=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image /73366705/STK417_banking_money_1.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;插图：Hugo Herrera / The Verge&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;ybCONI&quot;>;国税局免费申报计划将再持续五年。 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.irs.gov/newsroom/irs-announces-extension-of-free-file-program-through-2029&quot;>;该机构已宣布&lt;/a>;将通过以下方式扩展该计划： 2029 年 10 月，允许人们免费向 IRS 合作伙伴之一报税。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;vZ4v1z&quot;>;免费报税计划最近在 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www&quot; 事件之后受到更多关注.theverge.com/2020/1/1/21045779/irs-turbotax-free-file-hr-block-tax-preparation-new-rules&quot;>;国税局在 2020 年更改了规则&lt;/a>;，以防止报税者隐瞒他们的免费服务。两者&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2021/7/17/22581587/turbotax-parent-company-intuit-opts-out-irs-free-file-program&quot;>;TurboTax&lt;/a>;此后，H&amp;R Block 退出了免费文件计划，TurboTax 所有者 Intuit 支付了 1.41 亿美元的赔偿&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2022/5/4/23057463/intuit-141- Million-agreement-new-york-attorney-general-turbotax-free&quot;>;因为它&lt;/a>;“欺骗了数以百万计的低收入美国人，让他们无法享受免费报税服务”，纽约总检察长利蒂西亚·詹姆斯 (Letitia James) 表示。&lt; /p>; &lt;div class=&quot;c-float-left c-float-hang&quot;>;&lt;aside id=&quot;WLVd09&quot;>;&lt;div data-anthem-component=&quot;readmore&quot; data-anthem-component-data=&#39;{&quot; Stories&quot;:[{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;FTC 法官判定 Intuit 的“免费”TurboTax 广告确实误导了消费者&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2023/9/8/23864538/turbotax-intuit -ftc-deceptive-practices-free-tax-filing&quot;},{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;如果 Intuit 欺骗您支付 TurboTax“免费版”的费用，它就欠您钱&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.ftc-deceptive-practices-free-tax-filing&quot;} theverge.com/2022/5/4/23057463/intuit-141-million-agreement-new-york-attorney-general-turbotax-free&quot;}]}&#39;>;&lt;/div>;&lt;/aside>;&lt;/div>; &lt; p id=&quot;e3VmfC&quot;>;IRS 免费文件已经存在 20 多年了。 2023 年，调整后总额的纳税人...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/5/23/24163530/irs-free-file-tax-program -扩展&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/5/23/24163530/irs-free-file-tax-program-extended" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/5/23/24163530/irs-free-file-tax-program-extended</id><author><name>艾玛·罗斯</name></author></entry></feed>